snippet.title: Suspicious Downpour - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1657170/
Download on Itch.io here: https://fatherbeno.itch.io/suspicious-downpour


Welcome to hanawiti forest, a popular location for adventurous backpackers. Pitch a tent and stay the night in our lush and beautiful backyard. Enjoy the wildlife, enjoy the scenery and have an eye out for Mr. Wilson. Just make sure you don’t get caught in a rainstorm.  

WARNING: Don’t feed the wildlife and don’t pack any meat.

Credits:
Hamish Oliver (HamishOliver) - Music, Sound, Design
Benjamin Gulliver (fatherbeno) - UI/UX, Design, Programming
Jared Bakker (Sugoi Yellow) - Graphics, Design, Programming
